115
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:55,240
a package from one part of the US one day, and deliver it to another the next day.

116
00:07:55,240 --> 00:08:00,680
Amazon, meanwhile, built their prime brand off the promise of two-day delivery—ordering

117
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:03,800
a package on a Monday and getting it on a Wednesday, for example.

118
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:08,560
While they've sent straight from the rigidness of that system, the fastest shipping they'll

119
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:13,340
